title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Ramcharan tries to provoke Madan against Sugna and her son. Shyam fetches Sugna. Sugna's family bid her warm farewell. Sugna's family worry about Sugna.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Sugna and Shyam are happy together. Bhairon Singh is worried about Jagiya's studies. Bhairon Singh gets angry at Jagiya for his casual behaviour towards his studies. Daadisa gets angry at Anandi.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Shyam makes excuses to meet Sugna. Daadisa gets angry at Anandi for not doing household work. Jagiya has a nightmare about his studies. Anandi finds a way to prepare Jagiya for his examination.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Daadisa screams at Sumitra for giving Anandi the same opportunities that her son enjoys. Gehna and Sumitra tolerate the atrocities and injustice quietly. Daadisa makes Anandi do lots of work.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Anandi burns her hand, but still finds a way to write her exam. Bhagwati argues with Khajaan Singh for his behaviour. Daadisa scolds Jagiya infront of the whole family as he was feeding Anandi.

title: Balika Vadhu
subTitle: Jagdish gets caught cheating in his test paper. The master let him go after taking his money. Sugna is scared of her child being snatched away due to the previous temple incident.
